    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK44">
<l>paḻiyañcip pāttū ṇuṭaittāyiṉ vāḻkkai</l>
<l>vaḻiyeñca leññāṉṟu mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If, fearing disgrace, his life abounds with shared enjoyments,</l>
<l>his line will ever be without defect.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
